bham.leakiest

Class ReadFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • bham.leakiest.ReadFile

  • public class ReadFile
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the class that contains methods for reading a conditional probability matrix or a list of observations from a text file.
    Version:
    1.2
    Author:
    Tom Chothia, Yusuke Kawamoto, Chris Novakovic
